{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Siap Bertempur? Inilah Peralatan Perang Komikus Digital CIAYO Comics","content":"<p>Halo <em>bro sis, </em>kalian udah pasti pada tahu situs komik Indonesia CIAYO Comics dong. Banyak dari kalian juga pasti udah baca komik-komik keren yang ada di <a href=\"http://ciayo.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ciayo.com</a>. Komik-komik di ciayo.com semua bikinan komikus-komikus asli Indonesia <em>lho</em>! Nah, itu artinya, kamu juga bisa bikin komik kayak mereka!</p>\n<p>Sebelum kamu mulai bikin komik impian kamu, pasti butuh alat menggambar buat bikin komik dong. Apa aja sih alat menggambar yang dibutuhkan buat bikin komik digital Indonesia ala CIAYO Comics? Di artikel ini, kita tanya-tanya sama salah satu komikus handal kita <strong>Mario</strong>. Mario ini adalah komikus komik action paling keren di ciayo.com <a href=\"https://ciayo.com/comic/fourger\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Fourger Inc</strong></a>. Nah, Mario udah kasih <em>list </em>nih peralatan perang apa aja yg dia butuhkan buat bikin komik digital Fourger Inc.</p>\n<h2>Ini Dia Alat Menggambar Komikus Fourger Inc!</h2>\n<h3><strong>Komputer atau Laptop</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1796\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1796\" data-attachment-id=\"1796\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/attachment/body-4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Laptop (CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Laptop (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-4-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-4-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1796 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alat Menggambar Komikus komputer\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-4-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-4-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1796\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laptop (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Menurut Mario, ini adalah alat menggambar komikus terpenting yang harus dipakai untuk membuat komik digital. Yah, kalau nggak ada komputer, gimana bisa bikin komik digital ya? Komputer ini nggak harus kamu beli lho, kamu bisa kok pakai komputer yang ada di warnet, di kampus, atau minjem punya temen. Asal jangan lupa komikmu disimpen di flash disk atau hard drive eksternal ya!</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/fourger-inc-kisah-empat-agen-rahasia-swasta-di-belakang-layar-peristiwa-trending/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fourger Inc: Kisah Empat Agen Rahasia Swasta Di Belakang Layar Peristiwa Trending</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Software</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1798\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1798\" data-attachment-id=\"1798\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/attachment/body-6-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Adobe Photoshop (CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Adobe Photoshop (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-6-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-6-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1798 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alat Menggambar Komikus software\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-6-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-6-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1798\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Adobe Photoshop (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Nah kalau udah ada komputer, kamu juga butuh software di dalamnya. Software yang paling sering dipakai komikus adalah <strong>Adobe Photoshop</strong>. Di Photoshop ini, kamu bisa menggambar apapun yang kamu mau. Kamu bahkan bisa masukin gambar lain sebagai referensi untuk komik kamu. Kamu juga nggak perlu repot-repot ngehabisin banyak kertas buat sketsa komik, karena semuanya bisa dilakukan di Photoshop ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1797\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1797\" data-attachment-id=\"1797\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/attachment/body-5-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"SketchBook Pro (CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;SketchBook Pro (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1797 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alat Menggambar Komikus software\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1797\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">SketchBook Pro (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Khusus komik Fourger Inc, Mario juga pakai satu software khusus yaitu <strong>SketchBook Pro</strong>. Software ini digunakan oleh Mario khusus untuk menggambar detail arsitektur gedung, kendaraan, lanskap kota, dan berbagai benda mati lainnya. Menurutnya, software ini membantu banget membuat garis-garis di komiknya menjadi lebih keren</p>\n<h3><strong>Tablet Grafis</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1795\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1795\" data-attachment-id=\"1795\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/attachment/body-3-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-3-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tablet Grafis (CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tablet Grafis (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-3-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-3-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1795 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alat Menggambar Komikus tablet\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-3-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-3-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1795\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tablet Grafis (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalau komikus biasa, komiknya masih digambar di atas kertas, jadi mereka menggambar komiknya ya pakai pensil, tinta, dan pulpen. Kalau komik digital gimana dong? masa layar komputernya dicoret-coret? Ya pasti ngga dong. Mayoritas komikus digital pakai sebuah alat menggambar komikus yang namanya Tablet Grafis. Tablet Grafis ini adalah sebuah tablet persegi panjang yang berfungsi sebagai kanvas yang bisa dicoret-coret dengan pen yang disertakan. Nanti apapun yang kamu gambar di sana, akan muncul di layar komputer kamu. <em>Keren ya</em>!</p>\n<p>Tablet Grafis yang paling terkenal dipakai komikus adalah <strong>Wacom Intuos</strong>. Namun bagi kamu yang lebih sering mobile, bisa pakai tablet yang lainnya kok seperti <strong>iPad</strong> ,<b>Tablet Android</b>, dan <strong>Microsoft Surface</strong>. Bagi kamu yang mau pake surface selebar mungkin, bisa juga coba <strong>Microsoft Surface Studio</strong>. Yah budgetnya juga lebar sih.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tips-dan-langkah-membuat-komik-one-shot-dalam-format-webtoon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tips dan Langkah Membuat Komik One-Shot Dalam Format Webtoon</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Referensi Komik</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1794\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1794\" data-attachment-id=\"1794\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/attachment/body-2-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-2-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Komik Montage (CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Komik Montage (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-2-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-2-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1794 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alat Menggambar Komikus referensi\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-2-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-2-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1794\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Komik Montage (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sekarang peralatan untuk bikin komik digital udah lengkap nih, tapi bingung mau bikin komik apa? Pertama-tama kamu harus cari ide dong. Nah, salah satu cara untuk mendapatkan ide adalah dengan mencari referensi dari komik-komik lain. Mario pun udah baca banyak banget komik-komik action lainnya untuk mendapatkan referensi gambar Fourger Inc, salah satunya adalah komik <strong>Montage </strong>karya <strong>Jun Watanabe</strong>. Menurut Mario, style dari komik misteri ini berguna banget untuk menggugah ide-ide kreatif dalam teknik penggambaran Fourger Inc.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1799\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1799\" data-attachment-id=\"1799\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siap-bertempur-inilah-peralatan-perang-komikus-digital-ciayo-comics/attachment/body1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Perlengkapan Perang Komikus (CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Perlengkapan Perang Komikus (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1799 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1.jpg\" alt=\"Alat Menggambar Komikus meja\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1799\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Perlengkapan Perang Komikus (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Nah udah pada paham kan alat menggambar komikus yang digunakan oleh komikus-komikus digital ciayo.com. Udah punya alatnya? Siap bikin komik? Kirim aja ke <a href=\"mailto:hello@ciayo.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hello@ciayo.com</a>. Siapa tahu komik kamu bisa nangkring di sebelah Fourger Inc.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"f1653844-c8fc-5702-b5e3-d59e30ce7458"}}}